Numbers play a huge role in the life of every person on earth from getting the date and time of birth to the number of steps taken per day and time of sleep.
Throughout our life we form meaningful dates related to events that have a special significance for us like first step of the child, first day at school, first love, first work and anothers....
But there are those that every man on the planet remembers.
